{"tid":2456951,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國一拳超人反遭KO！UFC生涯最慘敗仗","createTime":"2021-03-22T09:40:51.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T06:50:16.000Z","uid":75969,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"7edf15d4fba6daa676cc07e508c409378597cf0c","tid":2456951,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T09:40:51.000Z","msg":"〔體育中心／綜合報導〕UFC拉斯維加斯賽事，中國「一拳超人」宋克南意外慘敗，首回合2分20秒就遭美國地主悍將葛瑞芬（Max Griffin）組合拳KO倒地，一面倒的擂台戰況，也引發各界熱議。<br />\n<br />\n現年31歲的宋克南，轉戰UFC戰績出色，此役之前4勝1負、3度KO對手，立技重拳打法威力十足，讓他擁有「一拳超人」外號，只不過，臨場面對年長4歲、原本UFC戰績3勝6負的葛瑞芬，結局卻出乎各界預料。開賽宋克南刺拳搭配腿法控制距離，尋找機會頻頻攻擊，卻始終無法突破奏效，宋克南一次低掃腿進攻不成，反遭對手還擊頭部，退了幾步至八角鐵籠邊，緊接著葛瑞芬衝上前連續猛攻壓制，右拳打中其下巴直接KO，宋克南倒地後葛瑞芬再補一拳，隨即遭裁判制止。<br />\n<br />\n這是宋克南第一次在UFC被KO，<span class=\"red\">賽後中國媒體解釋，受武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情影響，他的訓練、出賽計畫都被打斷，加上首次赴美參賽及時差影響，種種不利因素才導致「一拳超人」慘敗。 <br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/CMq7_NGptKj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMq7_NGptKj&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbcVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=8c50a678\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMq7_NGptKj&h=c6e3d188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/CMq7_NGptKj</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3474509\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3474509&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbcVJ7iodhWXw1gkpPdYK6Sw%3D&h=5f2acf5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbreakingnews%2F3474509&h=771b75b1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://sports.ltn.com.tw/news/breakingnews/3474509</a>"},{"pid":"f9ee277211c83670dcf714b96b05b6100b5f8edc","tid":2456951,"uid":70439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T09:42:06.000Z","msg":"山寨超人？"},{"pid":"1e4be18278047cd831b1fbf2d1b1669fd7a087a0","tid":2456951,"uid":35296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited